{"type":"section","nativeType":"section","number":"32310","heading":"New Car Assessment Program roadmap","label":"32310 New Car Assessment Program roadmap","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s32310","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/stVI/ptC/ch323","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs32310","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":["Editorial Notes","References in TextThe date of enactment of this section, referred to in subsec. (a), is the date of enactment of , which was approved .Pub. L. 117–58Nov. 15, 2021"],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"a","heading":".—Establishment","label":"a .—Establishment","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s32310/a","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s32310","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs32310%2Fa","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":"Not later than 1 year after the date of enactment of this section, and not less frequently than once every 4 years thereafter, the Secretary of Transportation (referred to in this section as the “Secretary”) shall establish a roadmap for the implementation of the New Car Assessment Program of the National Highway Traffic Safety Administration.","notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[]},{"type":"subsection","nativeType":"subsection","number":"b","heading":".—Requirements","label":"b .—Requirements","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s32310/b","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s32310","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs32310%2Fb","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"amendments":[],"effectiveDate":null,"children":[{"type":"paragraph","nativeType":"paragraph","number":"1","heading":null,"label":"1","identifier":"/us/usc/t49/s32310/b/1","parentIdentifier":"/us/usc/t49/s32310/b","sourceUrl":"https://uscode.house.gov/view.xhtml?req=%2Fus%2Fusc%2Ft49%2Fs32310%2Fb%2F1","sourceRelease":"119-100","text":null,"notes":[],"ame